<br>
Allow me to point out that the rule you have provided above is actually incorrect however. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
If you or your group do 1 pt or more damage to the mob, pet takes no XP.<br>
If the pet does 100% of the damage to the mob, the pet takes 75% XP.<br>
<br>
